Enter Your gender(male/female)female
Enter Your age:20
Enter Your SPR number:9102
Enter Your phone number:909090909
Enter Ypur  Height in feet:5.5
Enter your weight in kg:81
Are you a college student?(yes/no):yes
Enter how many siblings you have(0-5):0

